name: TimberClicker
description:
TIMBER CLICKER!

A game made in 0 hours, in a tram, dedicated to the creators of Timberman.

Experience the blissful life of a timber man in a paradise, where the branches are always on the other side! Reinvest your earnings into stationary saws, that do your work for you, in TimberClicker - the worlds worst and only combination of TimberMan and CookieClicker!
